---
title: Moroccan Honey Chicken Breast with Roast Veggie Couscous, Currants & Lemon Yoghurt
description: We love the way honey caramelises in a pan, lending a crispy, sticky finish to chicken. We’ve used chicken breast here
because it packs a fantastic flavour, remains moist as it cooks and complements the bed of delicious roast veggie
couscous that comes with it.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
